{"tid":272050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【寒售寒冬】廣東道地舖丟空年半50萬租出 劈租72%","createTime":"2017-06-05T14:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T14:34:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28cf07c1937f5617ec8bde7e1ea0eaf1d7a8e4f5","tid":272050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"即時財經  2017-06-05 20:55:48 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n廣東道一個丟空年半的地舖，近期以50萬元租予參茸店，租金勁跌逾72%。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n溥儀眼鏡在2012年租用此舖，月租曾高達180萬元。(蘋果日報)<br />\n核心零售區尖沙嘴廣東道再現大幅劈租！原由高級眼鏡店溥儀眼鏡承租的尖沙嘴廣東道116至120號海威商業中心地下A舖，約1,000方呎，在2012年舖租高峯期以180萬元承租，呎租高達1,800元。舖位最新以50萬元租予參茸店，呎租500元，最新租金較之前大減72.2%。<br />\n<br />\n自由行豪客大減，廣東道人流亦大不如前，溥儀眼鏡只租用上址三年，於2015年10月底已結束分店。業主在租客遷出前，曾叫價280萬元放租，惟在溥儀眼鏡離去後已降價至150萬元。不過舖位市道大幅下滑，業主幾乎每三個月調低一次叫價，都無新租客承租，今年初已調低至60萬元。<br />\n<br />\n近期業主再度減多10萬元，終以50萬元獲租客承租，月租是全廣東道最低的其中一間。此舖見證過自由行效應的輝煌歷史，業主之前丟空年半，現重新租出每月少收130萬元租金，以兩年租期計，即合共約3,120萬元。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=Y%2BpPVQe0OTvO2ypC3%2BqKHm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a02d7e45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a>"},{"pid":"f8e7a87c44ecddbbb6653d673c5617beb9405524","tid":272050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170605&amp;guid=56788025&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170605%26guid%3D56788025%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=Y%2BpPVQe0OTvO2ypC3%2BqKHm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=79d855e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170605%26guid%3D56788025%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=7ac15c1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170605&amp;guid=56788025&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"05b355de19ebecaab6055033d08223b6b00d393a","tid":272050,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"業主在租客遷出前，曾叫價280萬元放租<br />\n<br />\n..........."},{"pid":"ca34c1d522ea2333c2632c7c97236d15b3b0f4ae","tid":272050,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"溥儀眼鏡在2012年租用此舖，月租曾高達180萬元<br />\n<br />\n賣幾多先夠回本?"},{"pid":"726954fbb58a59f5527a2305a73e3e7287fe21a8","tid":272050,"uid":7150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溥儀眼鏡在2012年租用此舖，月租曾高達180萬元<br />\n<br />\n賣幾多先夠回本?</blockquote><br />\n賣下廣告都要錢啦"},{"pid":"8fb89302a9974f73b4f3f59d01311db65e396bc0","tid":272050,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09e6e66307e8ad114833b30b474ced5584abb364","tid":272050,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"做乜唔企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f038b04940871b34eb3ae13bc7ad564bc2ff29a3","tid":272050,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明賣眼鏡係暴利</blockquote><br />\n暴極都好難交180萬啦"},{"pid":"fe50fc994cb836c7e74c3686c1acfe7e678978da","tid":272050,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>證明賣眼鏡係暴利</blockquote><br />\n暴極都好難交180萬啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開譚仔都要執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25899677140df608f3b0e768222387a06ddee24e","tid":272050,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"做業主真係勁賺，痴線"},{"pid":"fa23fc4ef6c84bbc23d0cf7b7be4d5918c9f40c8","tid":272050,"uid":11299